        "description": "ANSYS CFX 15 release candidate build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2, configured with SST k-omega turbulence model, power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model (Giersiepen constants), 5.2M hexahedral element mesh, second-order advection scheme, and convergence criterion RMS residuals < 1e-5. This configuration was used for all validation runs submitted with the credibility package. The transition from rc2 to the final build 2026-q1-build-7 involved only a correction to the post-processing colormap rendering pipeline; no solver kernel, turbulence model, or blood damage model source files were modified. Engineering judgment holds the two builds to be computationally equivalent for this COU.",
