    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH predictions within 12% of experimental measurements across all operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The solver configuration used for validation (build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2) is considered by the assessment team to be computationally equivalent to the released build (2026-q1-build-7), as the intervening patch addressed only post-processing display rendering and did not modify any solver or physics model code. On this basis the credibility package is accepted and the CFD model is judged fit for the stated COU.",
